rong\">TINY</Text>\n            <Figure size=\"tiny\">\n                <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n            </Figure>\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">SMALL</Text>\n            <Figure size=\"small\">\n                <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n            </Figure>\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">MEDIUM</Text>\n            <Figure size=\"medium\">\n                <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n            </Figure>\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">LARGE</Text>\n            <Figure size=\"large\">\n                <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n            </Figure>\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">HUGE</Text>\n            <Figure size=\"huge\">\n                <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n            </Figure>\n        </div>\n    </Stack>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.figure-size figure[data-size] > img) {\n        max-width: max-content;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Figure Size"},{"identifier":"figure-fit","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Figure,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"figure-fit\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Figure variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">CONTAIN</Text>\n        <Figure fit=\"contain\" variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">COVER</Text>\n        <Figure fit=\"cover\" variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">FILL</Text>\n        <Figure fit=\"fill\" variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">NONE</Text>\n        <Figure fit=\"none\" variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">SCALE-DOWN</Text>\n        <Figure fit=\"scale-down\" variation=\"icon\">\n            <img src={IMAGE_BACKGROUND} />\n        </Figure>\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.figure-fit img) {\n        width: 12rem;\n        height: 18rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Figure Fit"}],"title":"Figure"},"render":"<h1 id=\"figure\">Figure</h1>\n<p><code>Figure</code> is a multimedia container Component, providing modifications for things such as images and videos.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Figure<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"shape\">Shape</h2>\n<p>You can modify the shape of the child content via the <code>shape</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-shape?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-shape?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"size\">Size</h2>\n<p>You can modify the size of the child content between five presets via the <code>size</code> property. Along with separate set of sizes meant for icon-sized content by including <code>variation=&quot;icon&quot;</code>.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-size?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-size?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"fit\">Fit</h2>\n<p>You can change how the child content is stretched across the <code>Figure</code> container via the <code>fit</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-fit?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/embedded/figure/figure-fit?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}